languages.text: "Снова-здорово — давайте верить остроухим и спасать ксеносов! Мы же не учимся на своих ошибках, не-ет". {n}Жалобный стон адресован скорее самой Джай, нежели вашим ушам.{/n}
"Here we go again! Trusting the pointy-eared ones and saving xenos! We don't learn from our mistakes, do we? Nah, of course not!" {n}Jae's plaintive groan is directed more at herself than you.{/n}

languages.text: 「またかよ！とんがり耳を信じて異種族を助けるなんて！失敗から学ばないのかって？もちろん、学ばないね！」{n}ジェイは物憂げに不満を漏らすが、その矛先はあなたではなく彼女自身に向けられている。{/n}
languages.original_text: "Here we go again! Trusting the pointy-eared ones and saving xenos! We don't learn from our mistakes, do we? Nah, of course not!" {n}Jae's plaintive groan is directed more at herself than you.{/n}

languages.text: “又来了！因为尖耳朵说了几句话，就跑过去救异形了！又来了！人类从来不明白什么叫做吸取教训，对不对？我看没错，就是不懂！”{n}婕伊在一旁怨气冲天，但她的怨气更多地是针对自己，而不是你。{/n}

languages.text: « Et c'est reparti ! Faire confiance aux oreilles pointues et sauver des xénos ! Nous n'apprenons pas de nos erreurs, pas vrai ? Non, bien sûr que non ! » {n}Le grognement de Jae s'adresse davantage à elle-même qu'à vous.{/n}
languages.original_text: "Here we go again! Trusting the pointy-eared ones and saving xenos! We don't learn from our mistakes, do we? Nah, of course not!" {n}Jae's plaintive groan is directed more at herself than you.{/n}

languages.text: «¡Otra vez con las mismas! ¡Confiando en orejudos y salvando xenos! No aprendemos, ¿eh? ¡Claro que no!». {n}El gemido quejumbroso de Jae se dirige más a sí misma que a ti.{/n}

languages.text: "Nicht schon wieder. Wir vertrauen den Spitzohren und retten Xenos! Wir lernen offenbar nichts aus unseren Fehlern, was? Nein, natürlich nicht!" {n}Jaes wehleidiges Stöhnen ist eher an sie selbst als an dich gerichtet.{/n}

languages.text: "İşte yine başladık! Sivri kulaklılara bel bağlayıp zeno kurtarıyoruz! Yanlışlarımızdan ders çıkarmak bize yasak mı acaba? Yasak herhâlde!" {n}Jae, senden ziyade kendi kendine ağlamaklı bir şekilde mırın kırın ediyor.{/n}
